00:11:40,033 --> 00:11:41,951
THEY CLAIM THEY KNOW
NOTHING ABOUT IT.

223
00:11:41,993 --> 00:11:43,537
THAT DOESN'T SEEM LIKELY,
DOES IT?

224
00:11:43,578 --> 00:11:45,539
I BELIEVE THEM.

225
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:47,666
I ADMIRE YOUR LOYALTY.

226
00:11:47,706 --> 00:11:49,792
WE THINK TERRA PRIME
IS INVOLVED,

227
00:11:49,834 --> 00:11:51,461
THAT THEY'RE
PLANNING SOMETHING.

228
00:11:51,503 --> 00:11:53,004
YOU JUST DON'T KNOW WHAT?

229
00:11:53,046 --> 00:11:56,007
WE SUSPECT IT HAS SOMETHING
TO DO WITH THE CHILD.

230
00:11:56,049 --> 00:11:58,801
FIND IT,
YOU'LL HAVE THE ANSWERS.

231
00:12:12,023 --> 00:12:14,067
YOU RECRUITED HER.

232
00:12:14,108 --> 00:12:16,027
I NEEDED HER EXPERTISE.

233
00:12:16,069 --> 00:12:17,445
I THOUGHT SHE WAS RELIABLE.

234
00:12:17,487 --> 00:12:19,656
OBVIOUSLY YOU WERE MISTAKEN.

235
00:12:19,698 --> 00:12:22,992
IF SHE'D TOLD THEM ANYTHING
TRULY DAMAGING, I THINK
WE'D KNOW IT BY NOW.

236
00:12:23,034 --> 00:12:25,662
WE CAN'T BE SURE
WHAT SHE TOLD THEM.

237
00:12:25,704 --> 00:12:29,123
ANYWAY, I'M MORE CONCERNED WITH
WHY SHE TURNED AWAY FROM US.

238
00:12:29,165 --> 00:12:32,085
I THINK THAT SHE MIGHT HAVE
BECOME ATTACHED TO THE PATIENT.

239
00:12:32,126 --> 00:12:33,961
SHE SPENT A GREAT DEAL OF TIME
CARING FOR HER.

240
00:12:34,003 --> 00:12:37,424
-AND WHAT ABOUT YOU?
-ME?

241
00:12:37,465 --> 00:12:40,468
YES. YOU'VE SPENT AS MUCH TIME
WITH THE CHILD AS SHE DID.

242
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:42,554
I FEEL NO DIFFERENTLY ABOUT IT

243
00:12:42,596 --> 00:12:45,056
THAN ANYONE ELSE
THAT I'VE TREATED.

244
00:12:47,308 --> 00:12:50,978
THIS ISN'T "ANYONE ELSE."
THIS IS AN ABOMINATION.

245
00:12:51,020 --> 00:12:54,566
AND WHEN THE TIME COMES,
IT WILL BE TREATED AS SUCH.

246
00:12:54,608 --> 00:12:57,318
I UNDERSTAND.

247
00:13:00,863 --> 00:13:04,951
WELL, I'M GONNA
MISS THIS PLACE.

248
00:13:04,992 --> 00:13:06,453
THE SIMPLICITY.

249
00:13:06,494 --> 00:13:10,373
THERE'S NO MIDDLE GROUND HERE.

250
00:13:10,415 --> 00:13:12,667
AND I CAN SEE THE EARTH.

251
00:13:15,128 --> 00:13:16,795
SEND IN GREAVES
ON YOUR WAY OUT.

252
00:13:16,837 --> 00:13:18,923
YES, SIR.

253
00:13:24,512 --> 00:13:26,097
I GAVE THE MEN
YOUR MESSAGE.

254
00:13:26,139 --> 00:13:28,182
WE'LL BE READY
AT A MOMENT'S NOTICE.

255
00:13:28,224 --> 00:13:30,268
TELL THEM I APPRECIATE
THEIR HARD WORK.

256
00:13:30,310 --> 00:13:33,146
-THEY ALREADY KNOW.
-THERE'S ONE OTHER THING.

257
00:13:33,187 --> 00:13:34,981
A LOOSE END THAT NEEDS TYING UP.

258
00:13:35,022 --> 00:13:39,026
PUT TOGETHER A GROUP, HAVE THEM
MEET ME AT THE THIRD JUNCTION,

259
00:13:39,068 --> 00:13:41,946
SAY, ONE HOUR.

260
00:13:41,988 --> 00:13:43,864
DONE.

261
00:13:46,117 --> 00:13:48,787
[ DOOR OPENS ]

262
00:13:54,167 --> 00:13:56,586
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

263
00:14:00,548 --> 00:14:02,883
THE TELLARITES ARE PUSHING FOR
AN EMBARGO AGAINST THE ORIONS.

264
00:14:02,925 --> 00:14:04,803
THEY CLAIM THEY'VE BEEN
ATTACKING THEIR FREIGHTERS.

265
00:14:04,843 --> 00:14:07,054
WE'VE TRADED WITH THE ORIONS
FOR CENTURIES.

266
00:14:07,096 --> 00:14:10,600
WE WOULD HAVE KNOWN
OF THESE ATTACKS.
IT'S TELLARITE SLANDER.

267
00:14:10,642 --> 00:14:12,686
YOU HAVE TO APPRECIATE
THEIR POINT OF VIEW.

268
00:14:12,727 --> 00:14:15,689
THE TELLARITES ONLY WANT TO
DEPRIVE US OF VALUABLE COMMERCE.

269
00:14:15,730 --> 00:14:18,983
CORIDAN WILL NEVER AGREE
TO ANY TRADE SANCTIONS.

270
00:14:19,025 --> 00:14:20,652
AMBASSADOR, CAPTAIN ARCHER.

271
00:14:20,694 --> 00:14:22,487
AMBASSADOR.

272
00:14:22,529 --> 00:14:26,491
I NEED TO CONTACT MY GOVERNMENT
ABOUT TODAY'S DEVELOPMENTS.

273
00:14:26,533 --> 00:14:28,242
EXCUSE ME.

274
00:14:30,036 --> 00:14:31,788
[ SIGHING ]
HOW CAN I HELP YOU?

275
00:14:31,830 --> 00:14:33,289
I WANT EVERYTHING STARFLEET HAS

276
00:14:33,331 --> 00:14:35,082
ON THE INVESTIGATION.

277
00:14:35,124 --> 00:14:37,001
WHY COME TO ME?

278
00:14:37,043 --> 00:14:39,128
BECAUSE THE CHIEF INVESTIGATOR
TURNED ME DOWN.

279
00:14:39,170 --> 00:14:40,588
YOU CAN CHANGE HIS MIND.

280
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:42,173
I CAN'T DO THAT.
I'M SORRY.

281
00:14:42,215 --> 00:14:45,510
SUSAN KHOURI
WAS A MEMBER OF TERRA PRIME.

282
00:14:46,845 --> 00:14:50,473
IF THAT'S TRUE,
IT'S EXTREMELY TROUBLING.

283
00:14:51,808 --> 00:14:54,561
NOT AS TROUBLING
AS SOMETHING ELSE WE LEARNED.

284
00:14:54,602 --> 00:14:56,270
YOU WERE ONCE A MEMBER.

285
00:14:58,857 --> 00:15:02,235
IT SEEMS YOU'RE DOING FAIRLY
WELL INVESTIGATING ON YOUR OWN.

286
00:15:02,276 --> 00:15:04,404
THAT'S WHY
YOU WANTED THIS KEPT QUIET.

287
00:15:04,445 --> 00:15:07,907
I'VE ALREADY EXPLAINED WHY
THERE WAS A NEED FOR SECRECY.

288
00:15:07,948 --> 00:15:10,034
I WAS VERY YOUNG
WHEN I JOINED TERRA PRIME.

289
00:15:10,076 --> 00:15:11,703
YOU WERE 18.

290
00:15:11,745 --> 00:15:13,788
DIDN'T YOU MAKE
ANY QUESTIONABLE CHOICES

291
00:15:13,830 --> 00:15:16,750
WHEN YOU WERE THAT AGE,
CAPTAIN?

292
00:15:18,042 --> 00:15:19,919
IT WAS A STUPID MISTAKE.
I WAS A FOOL.

293
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,588
MY FATHER HAD DIED
IN A FREIGHTER ACCIDENT,

294
00:15:21,629 --> 00:15:23,840
AND I BLAMED THE PILOT,
WHO HAPPENED TO BE DENOBULAN.

295
00:15:25,383 --> 00:15:27,886
WE ALL HAVE OUR DEMONS.
I'VE EXORCISED MINE.

296
00:15:27,927 --> 00:15:31,138
I DON'T CARE WHAT YOU DID
WHEN YOU WERE YOUNG, MINISTER.

297
00:15:31,180 --> 00:15:33,182
I NEED YOUR HELP.

298
00:15:33,224 --> 00:15:35,560
[ SCOFFS ]

299
00:15:35,602 --> 00:15:37,144
I UNDERESTIMATED YOU.

300
00:15:38,354 --> 00:15:40,064
I SUPPOSE I'M NOT
THE FIRST PERSON

301
00:15:40,106 --> 00:15:41,399
TO MAKE THAT MISTAKE.

302
00:15:42,859 --> 00:15:45,152
YOU'LL HAVE YOUR
CASE FILE WITHIN THE HOUR.

303
00:15:46,654 --> 00:15:48,197
THANK YOU.

304
00:16:01,795 --> 00:16:04,213
[ DOOR CHIMES ]

305
00:16:07,801 --> 00:16:12,639
HMM. CAN'T DECIDE -- IF I LIKE
YOU BETTER IN UNIFORM OR NOT.

306
00:16:13,848 --> 00:16:15,266
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

307
00:16:15,308 --> 00:16:18,185
I'VE BEEN ASSIGNED TO DO
A STORY ON<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

308
00:16:18,227 --> 00:16:21,731
HM. THEY CAN BUILD A SHIP
THAT GOES FASTER THAN LIGHT,

309
00:16:21,773 --> 00:16:24,651
-BUT THEY CAN'T GIVE
YOU A DECENT-SIZED ROOM.
-A STORY?

310
00:16:24,692 --> 00:16:26,945
IT'S TOLD FROM THE PERSPECTIVE
OF THE CREW.

311
00:16:26,986 --> 00:16:30,865
IT'LL COVER THE MISSIONS,
THE PERILS, LIFE IN SPACE.

312
00:16:30,907 --> 00:16:33,868
SO, SHALL WE START
WITH A TOUR?

313
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:36,996
-I'VE GOT SOME WORK TO DO.
-YOU'RE NOT ON DUTY.

314
00:16:37,037 --> 00:16:38,331
GANNET.

315
00:16:38,372 --> 00:16:40,875
OKAY, SO...
[ SIGHS ]

316
00:16:40,917 --> 00:16:44,754
MAYBE...
I WASN'T ASSIGNED THE STORY.

317
00:16:46,005 --> 00:16:49,008
MAYBE I SUGGESTED THE IDEA
TO MY EDITOR.

318
00:16:49,049 --> 00:16:52,345
HE KNOW HOW YOU FEEL
ABOUT SPACE EXPLORATION?

319
00:16:52,386 --> 00:16:55,139
THAT IT'S THE "LAST VESTIGE
OF COLONIAL IMPULSE"?

320
00:16:55,181 --> 00:16:58,184
I ONLY SAID THAT TO KEEP YOU
FROM SIGNING ON TO THIS MISSION.

321
00:16:58,225 --> 00:16:59,644
FIND ANOTHER STORY TO DO.

322
00:16:59,686 --> 00:17:01,896
IT'S TOO LATE.
IT'S DUE A WEEK FROM TODAY.

323
00:17:01,938 --> 00:17:04,440
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE
TO FIND ANOTHER SOURCE
FOR YOUR INFORMATION.

324
00:17:04,482 --> 00:17:06,066
WHY ARE YOU AVOIDING ME?

325
00:17:06,108 --> 00:17:09,236
CAN YOU GIVE ME ONE REASON
WHY I SHOULDN'T AVOID YOU?

326
00:17:09,278 --> 00:17:11,906
WE BOTH CALLED IT OFF.

327
00:17:11,948 --> 00:17:13,407
IT WAS A MUTUAL DECISION.

328
00:17:13,449 --> 00:17:15,827
AND IT LOOKS LIKE
YOU'VE CHANGED YOUR MIND.

329
00:17:15,869 --> 00:17:18,705
I HAVEN'T DECIDED YET.

330
00:17:18,746 --> 00:17:22,000
THAT'S THE FIRST
HONEST THING YOU'VE SAID.

331
00:17:23,710 --> 00:17:28,047
SO, REWARD ME
BY GIVING ME THAT TOUR.

332
00:17:30,466 --> 00:17:32,760
GOT A MINUTE?

333
00:17:32,802 --> 00:17:34,303
CERTAINLY.

334
00:17:34,345 --> 00:17:36,222
[ SIGHS ]

335
00:17:36,263 --> 00:17:38,391
THIS BABY...

336
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:42,896
CAN YOU TELL
IF IT'S A BOY OR A GIRL?

337
00:17:42,937 --> 00:17:44,188
IT'S A GIRL.

338
00:17:44,230 --> 00:17:46,858
A GIRL.

339
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:51,404
IS IT OKAY? I MEAN,
PART HUMAN AND PART VULCAN.

340
00:17:51,445 --> 00:17:55,616
VULCAN AND HUMAN PHYSIOLOGY
ARE NOT ALL THAT DISSIMILAR.

341
00:17:55,658 --> 00:17:57,618
FROM THE EVIDENCE I HAVE,
THERE'S NO REASON TO BELIEVE

342
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:59,495
SHE'S ANYTHING
BUT PERFECTLY HEALTHY.

343
00:17:59,537 --> 00:18:01,455
THAT'S GOOD TO HEAR.

344
00:18:01,497 --> 00:18:03,958
YOU'LL ALSO BE INTERESTED
TO KNOW SHE HAS YOUR EYES,

345
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,459
AND T'POL'S EARS.

346
00:18:05,501 --> 00:18:08,671
I-I-I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

347
00:18:08,713 --> 00:18:11,591
I'M IN SOMETHING OF A QUANDARY
ABOUT IT MYSELF,

348
00:18:11,632 --> 00:18:14,510
ESPECIALLY SINCE T'POL'S
NEVER BEEN PREGNANT.

349
00:18:14,552 --> 00:18:16,971
SHE COULD HAVE GOTTEN PREGNANT
AND NOT TOLD ME ABOUT IT.

350
00:18:17,013 --> 00:18:18,973
AH.

351
00:18:19,015 --> 00:18:24,645
AND SHE HAD THE EMBRYO REMOVED,
ALSO WITHOUT YOUR KNOWLEDGE?

352
00:18:24,687 --> 00:18:27,857
I BELIEVE YOU KNOW THE ANSWER
TO THAT THEORY, COMMANDER.

353
00:18:29,149 --> 00:18:30,610
YEAH, I GUESS I DO.

354
00:18:30,651 --> 00:18:33,780
WE'LL GET TO THE BOTTOM
OF THIS SOON ENOUGH.

355
00:18:33,821 --> 00:18:38,367
UNTIL THEN, I SUGGEST YOU KEEP
ANY SUCH THEORIES TO YOURSELF.

356
00:18:41,245 --> 00:18:42,747
THAT'S GOOD ADVICE.

357
00:18:43,998 --> 00:18:45,416
YOU KNOW, MY FATHER

358
00:18:45,458 --> 00:18:48,502
ALWAYS WANTED A GRANDDAUGHTER.

359
00:18:48,544 --> 00:18:50,630
HE BUGGED MY SISTER
ABOUT IT CONSTANTLY.

360
00:18:50,671 --> 00:18:53,967
[ CHUCKLES ]
IT SEEMS HE GOT HIS WISH.

361
00:18:56,469 --> 00:18:57,595
WHEW.

362
00:18:57,637 --> 00:18:59,555
[<i> AUDIENCE APPLAUDING</i> ]

363
00:18:59,597 --> 00:19:02,182
<i>IN THE SHADOW OF THIS</i>
<i>INCALCULABLE DEVASTATION,</i>

364
00:19:02,224 --> 00:19:05,519
<i>WE FIND OURSELVES FACING</i>
<i>A COLOSSAL CHALLENGE.</i>

365
00:19:05,561 --> 00:19:08,815
<i>THERE'S AN ENTIRE WORLD</i>
<i>TO REBUILD.</i>

366
00:19:08,856 --> 00:19:13,778
<i>NOT ONLY OUR CITIES AND HOMES,</i>
<i>BUT MANKIND ITSELF!</i>

367
00:19:13,820 --> 00:19:17,406
<i>NOW IS NOT THE TIME FOR</i>
<i>TIMIDITY AND SECOND-GUESSING.</i>

368
00:19:17,448 --> 00:19:19,784
<i>WE CANNOT AFFORD</i>
<i>TO DOUBT OURSELVES.</i>

369
00:19:19,826 --> 00:19:21,577
THE THIRD WORLD WAR
HAD JUST ENDED,

370
00:19:21,619 --> 00:19:24,413
AND THE CEASE-FIRE
WAS BARELY 2 YEARS OLD.

371
00:19:24,455 --> 00:19:27,541
<i>UNLESS WE ACT DECISIVELY,</i>

372
00:19:27,583 --> 00:19:31,420
<i>WE WILL PASS ON THE SCARS</i>
<i>OF MUTATION AND DECAY</i>

373
00:19:31,462 --> 00:19:33,380
<i>TO FUTURE GENERATIONS.</i>

374
00:19:33,422 --> 00:19:36,926
-COLONEL GREEN.
-COLONEL GREEN.

375
00:19:36,968 --> 00:19:39,595
ONE OF THE MANY MEN
HISTORY HAS MISUNDERSTOOD.

376
00:19:39,637 --> 00:19:44,100
<i>FOR THE SAKE OF OUR CHILDREN</i>
<i>AND OUR CHILDREN'S CHILDREN,</i>

377
00:19:44,142 --> 00:19:49,522
<i>WE MUST REJECT THE IMPURE</i>
<i>AND CAST IT OUT!</i>

378
00:19:49,563 --> 00:19:51,941
[<i> CHEERS AND APPLAUSE</i> ]

379
00:19:51,983 --> 00:19:53,484
[ BEEPS ]

380
00:19:53,526 --> 00:19:55,611
BEFORE MY FATHER DIED
AND LEFT ME THIS FACILITY,

381
00:19:55,653 --> 00:19:58,156
I WAS STUDYING
TO BE AN HISTORIAN.

382
00:19:58,197 --> 00:20:00,992
UNTIL I HAD
A VERY VERBAL CONFRONTATION

383
00:20:01,034 --> 00:20:02,910
WITH A CERTAIN PROFESSOR
WHO CLAIMED THAT GREEN

384
00:20:02,952 --> 00:20:05,997
WAS NOTHING MORE
THAN A GENOCIDAL MADMAN.

385
00:20:06,039 --> 00:20:07,832
SOUNDS LIKE WE HAD
THE SAME PROFESSOR.

386
00:20:07,874 --> 00:20:09,834
GREEN EUTHANIZED
HUNDREDS OF THOUSANDS

387
00:20:09,876 --> 00:20:11,878
WHO WERE AFFLICTED
WITH RADIATION DAMAGE.

388
00:20:11,919 --> 00:20:13,713
THEIR MILLIONS OF DESCENDANTS

389
00:20:13,754 --> 00:20:15,506
WOULD HAVE ENDURED
HORRIBLE DISEASE,

390
00:20:15,548 --> 00:20:17,424
YET HISTORY --
HISTORY NEVER SAYS ANYTHING

391
00:20:17,466 --> 00:20:19,969
ABOUT THAT SUFFERING
THAT GREEN PREVENTED.

392
00:20:20,011 --> 00:20:22,388
GUESS IT ALL DEPENDS
ON WHO WRITES THE HISTORY.

393
00:20:22,429 --> 00:20:26,433
MAKES ME WONDER
IF I'LL BE REMEMBERED
WITH ANY MORE ACCURACY.

394
00:20:26,475 --> 00:20:29,020
I DON'T THINK YOU'RE
GOING TO BE MISUNDERSTOOD.

395
00:20:29,062 --> 00:20:32,982
REALLY? SOMETIMES I'M NOT
CERTAIN I UNDERSTAND MYSELF.

396
00:20:33,024 --> 00:20:37,444
WE DID WHAT WE HAD TO DO,
NOT WHAT WE WANTED TO DO.

397
00:20:37,486 --> 00:20:40,489
I'M SURE GREEN
TOLD HIMSELF THE SAME THING.

398
00:20:40,531 --> 00:20:43,534
HE WAS RIGHT, AND SO ARE WE.

399
00:20:47,454 --> 00:20:49,749
DANIEL, YOU ARE A...

400
00:20:50,875 --> 00:20:52,376
WISE MAN.

401
00:20:54,170 --> 00:20:56,380
MEDICAL REPORT ON THE PATIENT.

402
00:20:56,422 --> 00:20:57,840
HER SYMPTOMS ARE GONE.
SHE'S 100%.

403
00:20:57,882 --> 00:20:59,759
THAT'S WONDERFUL.

404
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:01,219
WONDERFUL. THANK YOU.

405
00:21:06,099 --> 00:21:07,641
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

406
00:21:18,652 --> 00:21:20,446
THAT WAS SOME SERIOUS FLYING,

407
00:21:20,487 --> 00:21:22,281
TRYING TO KEEP
THE WARP FIELDS ALIGNED.

408
00:21:22,322 --> 00:21:24,450
<i>COLUMBIA</i> WAS 50 METERS
ABOVE US.

409
00:21:24,491 --> 00:21:26,953
ONE WRONG MOVE, AND WE WOULD
HAVE LOST COMMANDER TUCKER.

410
00:21:26,994 --> 00:21:28,537
HOW DID YOU KEEP YOUR COOL?

411
00:21:28,579 --> 00:21:30,289
WHEN I WAS STUDYING
TO BE A PILOT,

412
00:21:30,330 --> 00:21:32,583
I MEMORIZED SOMETHING
CHUCK YEAGER SAID --

413
00:21:32,625 --> 00:21:34,293
"I NEVER LET MYSELF BE AFRAID.

414
00:21:34,334 --> 00:21:37,964
I JUST FOCUS ON THE DIALS
AND CONCENTRATE ON FLYING."

415
00:21:38,005 --> 00:21:41,801
-THAT SIMPLE, HUH?
-MOST OF THE TIME,
SIMPLE WORKS BEST.

416
00:21:48,766 --> 00:21:51,685
THESE ARE THE SHUTTLEPODS.

417
00:21:51,727 --> 00:21:53,312
WHICH ONE DID YOU USE

418
00:21:53,353 --> 00:21:56,398
TO PENETRATE THE SPHERE
IN THE EXPANSE?

419
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:58,192
SHUTTLEPOD 1.

420
00:22:02,571 --> 00:22:04,573
YOU WANT TO SEE INSIDE?

421
00:22:04,615 --> 00:22:06,366
IF IT'S OKAY.

422
00:22:11,413 --> 00:22:12,665
OHH!

423
00:22:12,706 --> 00:22:14,708
BEAUTIFUL LITTLE SHIP.

424
00:22:14,750 --> 00:22:17,295
I ALWAYS THOUGHT SO.

425
00:22:17,336 --> 00:22:20,298
UNFORTUNATELY, WE USE
THE SHUTTLEPODS LESS AND LESS.

426
00:22:20,339 --> 00:22:21,966
WHY?

427
00:22:22,008 --> 00:22:24,927
WE'RE GETTING MORE COMFORTABLE
WITH THE TRANSPORTER.

428
00:22:24,969 --> 00:22:27,305
MAKES SENSE. GETS YOU THERE
IN A FEW SECONDS.

429
00:22:27,345 --> 00:22:30,557
YEAH, BUT THERE'S
NO SKILL INVOLVED.

430
00:22:30,599 --> 00:22:32,685
MM-HMM.
NOTHING TO FLY.

431
00:22:32,726 --> 00:22:36,272
I'VE ALWAYS HAD A TENDENCY
TO GET ATTACHED TO MACHINES.

432
00:22:36,314 --> 00:22:39,317
IT'S CRAZY, BUT EVERY TIME
WE USE THE TRANSPORTER,

433
00:22:39,357 --> 00:22:42,444
I FEEL WE'RE KIND OF TURNING
OUR BACKS ON THESE GUYS.

434
00:22:42,486 --> 00:22:46,406
YOU CAN'T MAKE A CHOICE WITHOUT
LEAVING SOMETHING BEHIND.

435
00:22:49,285 --> 00:22:50,953
WHEN I SAW YOU
AT THAT CONFERENCE,

436
00:22:50,995 --> 00:22:54,165
I STARTED THINKING
ABOUT THINGS,

437
00:22:54,207 --> 00:22:55,541
DECISIONS I'VE MADE.

438
00:22:55,582 --> 00:22:57,960
IS IT MY IMAGINATION,

439
00:22:58,002 --> 00:23:00,129
OR ARE YOU ACTUALLY
OPENING UP TO ME?

440
00:23:00,171 --> 00:23:02,798
-DON'T DO THAT.
-WHAT?

441
00:23:02,840 --> 00:23:04,466
WHENEVER THINGS
GET A LITTLE SERIOUS,

442
00:23:04,508 --> 00:23:06,260
YOU ALWAYS
TURN IT INTO A JOKE.

443
00:23:06,302 --> 00:23:07,636
[ SIGHS ]

444
00:23:09,429 --> 00:23:10,973
IT'S A BAD HABIT.

445
00:23:14,727 --> 00:23:16,229
I HAVE A LOT OF THOSE.

446
00:23:25,821 --> 00:23:28,115
HERE'S ANOTHER ONE.

447
00:23:28,157 --> 00:23:31,744
WHEN I'M ATTRACTED TO SOMEONE,
I CAN'T HIDE IT FOR LONG.

448
00:23:33,704 --> 00:23:36,582
YOU AND YOUR BAD HABITS.

449
00:23:44,924 --> 00:23:47,385
THE AUTOPSY DATA CONFIRMS
WHAT WE ALREADY KNEW.

450
00:23:47,425 --> 00:23:50,388
SUSAN KHOURI WAS KILLED
BY PHASE-PISTOL FIRE.

451
00:23:50,428 --> 00:23:52,806
THE CASE FILE CONTAINS
VERY LITTLE ELSE
IN THE WAY OF EVIDENCE.

452
00:23:52,848 --> 00:23:56,227
SOME BIOGRAPHICAL
DATA ON KHOURI.
MOST OF IT'S OUT OF DATE.

453
00:23:56,269 --> 00:23:58,645
THEY DON'T EVEN KNOW WHERE SHE'D
BEEN LIVING FOR THE PAST YEAR.

454
00:23:58,687 --> 00:24:01,023
IT'S LIKE SHE DROPPED
OFF THE FACE OF THE EARTH.

455
00:24:01,065 --> 00:24:03,859
-THAT MAY BE
EXACTLY WHAT HAPPENED.
-YOU KNOW SOMETHING?

456
00:24:03,901 --> 00:24:06,279
HER BLOOD HAD ELEVATED LEVELS
OF GROWTH HORMONE.

457
00:24:06,320 --> 00:24:09,365
I RAN SOME MORE TESTS AND FOUND
TRACES OF MYOFIBRILIN.

458
00:24:09,407 --> 00:24:12,952
THAT'S WHAT THEY PRESCRIBE
FOR EXTENDED ZERO-G MISSIONS.

459
00:24:12,993 --> 00:24:15,746
IT'S HARDLY USED ANYMORE,
OUTSIDE OF MILITARY EXERCISES,

460
00:24:15,788 --> 00:24:17,831
NOT SINCE THE INVENTION
OF ARTIFICIAL GRAVITY.

461
00:24:17,873 --> 00:24:19,917
IT IS STILL GIVEN
TO WORKERS IN REMOTE PLACES

462
00:24:19,959 --> 00:24:21,961
WHERE ARTIFICIAL GRAVITY
ISN'T PRACTICAL.

463
00:24:22,002 --> 00:24:23,587
LIKE MINING COLONIES.

464
00:24:23,629 --> 00:24:25,965
THE NEAREST ONE IS ORPHEUS,
ON THE MOON.

465
00:24:26,006 --> 00:24:29,260
I HAVE HEARD THAT
THE MOON IS A HOTBED
OF TERRA PRIME ACTIVITY.

466
00:24:29,302 --> 00:24:33,555
YOU KNOW, I THINK TRAVIS HAS
A FRIEND WHO WORKED ON ORPHEUS.

467
00:24:33,597 --> 00:24:36,309
HE MIGHT BE ABLE TO GET
A COUPLE OF US INSIDE.

468
00:24:36,350 --> 00:24:39,686
WE COULD PAY A LITTLE VISIT,
UNDERCOVER.

469
00:24:39,728 --> 00:24:42,189
I WANT TO BE A PART
OF THAT VISIT.

470
00:24:42,231 --> 00:24:44,317
I'D LIKE TO VOLUNTEER, AS WELL.

471
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:47,653
TELL TRAVIS
TO SEE WHAT HE CAN DO.

472
00:24:47,694 --> 00:24:49,696
YES, SIR.

473
00:24:55,702 --> 00:24:58,580
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

474
00:25:14,805 --> 00:25:16,974
CAPTAIN'S STARLOG, SUPPLEMENTAL.

475
00:25:17,016 --> 00:25:19,143
WITH HELP
FROM TRAVIS'S CONTACT,

476
00:25:19,185 --> 00:25:20,894
TRIP AND T'POL
HAVE BEEN PROCESSED

477
00:25:20,936 --> 00:25:23,605
INTO THE ORPHEUS
MINING FACILITY.

478
00:25:23,647 --> 00:25:26,066
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

479
00:25:33,699 --> 00:25:36,785
[ MACHINE WHIRRING ]

480
00:25:43,125 --> 00:25:46,670
THIS IS THE SECOND TIME
WE'VE BEEN THROUGH HERE.
I'VE SEEN ALL THIS BEFORE.

481
00:25:46,712 --> 00:25:49,840
WE STILL HAVE 20 MINUTES
BEFORE WE HAVE TO REPORT
TO THE FOREMAN.

482
00:25:49,882 --> 00:25:52,134
MAYBE YOU DOWNLOADED
AN OUTDATED MAP.

483
00:25:52,176 --> 00:25:53,760
THE MAP IS CORRECT.

484
00:25:53,802 --> 00:25:55,846
MAYBE YOU'RE
READING IT WRONG.

485
00:25:55,888 --> 00:25:57,890
WE CAN ASK FOR DIRECTIONS.

486
00:25:57,931 --> 00:25:59,850
GIVE ME THAT.

487
00:26:05,147 --> 00:26:06,648
I THINK I KNOW
WHAT THE PROBLEM IS.

488
00:26:06,690 --> 00:26:09,443
-WHAT?
-WE'RE LOST.

489
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:13,697
-LET'S TRY THAT DIRECTION.
-ANY PARTICULAR REASON?

490
00:26:13,739 --> 00:26:16,867
IT'S THE ONLY TUNNEL
I DON'T RECOGNIZE.

491
00:26:20,746 --> 00:26:22,164
TRIP...

492
00:26:22,206 --> 00:26:23,874
I THINK WE'RE GETTING THERE.

493
00:26:23,916 --> 00:26:27,253
I KNOW YOU'RE NOT CONVINCED
I'VE TOLD YOU THE TRUTH

494
00:26:27,294 --> 00:26:30,256
-ABOUT THE CHILD.
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

495
00:26:30,297 --> 00:26:32,758
YOU THINK I MIGHT HAVE GOTTEN
PREGNANT WITHOUT YOUR KNOWLEDGE.

496
00:26:32,799 --> 00:26:34,927
I NEVER SAID THAT.

497
00:26:34,968 --> 00:26:36,345
I KNOW.

498
00:26:36,387 --> 00:26:38,305
YOU'VE BEEN TALKING TO PHLOX.

499
00:26:38,347 --> 00:26:40,724
NO. HAVE YOU?

500
00:26:40,766 --> 00:26:44,270
LOOK, IT'S BECAUSE
YOU'RE VULCAN, ISN'T IT,

501
00:26:44,311 --> 00:26:46,522
-THAT YOU KNOW ALL THIS?
-I BELIEVE SO.

502
00:26:46,564 --> 00:26:48,857
I AM SICK AND TIRED
OF THIS BOND WE'VE GOT.

503
00:26:48,899 --> 00:26:51,735
I DON'T PARTICULARLY
ENJOY IT, EITHER.

504
00:26:51,777 --> 00:26:53,320
LISTEN, FOR THE LAST TIME,

505
00:26:53,362 --> 00:26:56,782
AND FOR THE RECORD,
I DO BELIEVE YOU.

506
00:26:56,823 --> 00:27:00,702
AND IF YOU GET ANY
MORE FEELINGS -- WHAT?

507
00:27:01,912 --> 00:27:03,330
THERE IT IS.

508
00:27:03,372 --> 00:27:05,749
COME ON, LET'S GO.

509
00:27:11,046 --> 00:27:14,258
I'M GLAD WE FINALLY
LEFT THE SHUTTLEPOD.

510
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:16,176
I THOUGHT YOU LIKED SHUTTLEPODS.

511
00:27:16,218 --> 00:27:17,761
I LIKE FLYING THEM.

512
00:27:17,803 --> 00:27:21,140
HMM. SURE FELT
LIKE WE WERE FLYING.

513
00:27:30,732 --> 00:27:32,568
I HAVE A RULE.

514
00:27:32,610 --> 00:27:36,696
IF I'M IN BED WITH SOMEONE,
THEY HAVE TO BE IN BED WITH ME.

515
00:27:36,738 --> 00:27:38,324
WHAT WAS THAT?

516
00:27:38,365 --> 00:27:40,826
[ GRUNTS ]

517
00:27:40,867 --> 00:27:42,202
AH.

518
00:27:43,621 --> 00:27:46,664
YOU ARE NOT HERE.

519
00:27:46,706 --> 00:27:49,168
I'M JUST WORRIED
ABOUT SOME FRIENDS OF MINE.

520
00:27:49,209 --> 00:27:51,253
WANT TO TALK ABOUT IT?

521
00:27:51,295 --> 00:27:54,256
I'M UNDER ORDERS NOT
TO TALK ABOUT IT.

522
00:27:54,298 --> 00:27:56,800
THAT'S THE LAST THING
YOU SHOULD TELL A REPORTER.

523
00:27:56,842 --> 00:27:58,844
LET'S CHANGE THE SUBJECT.

524
00:27:58,885 --> 00:28:02,348
HOW COME YOU HAVEN'T
SETTLED DOWN?

525
00:28:02,389 --> 00:28:05,518
I'M NEVER GONNA SETTLE DOWN.

526
00:28:05,559 --> 00:28:09,021
IT DOESN'T MEAN I'M NOT GONNA
GET SERIOUS WITH SOMEONE...

527
00:28:09,062 --> 00:28:11,898
IF THE RIGHT CIRCUMSTANCE
COMES ALONG.

528
00:28:11,940 --> 00:28:14,652
AND WHAT CONSTITUTES
THE RIGHT CIRCUMSTANCE?

529
00:28:14,692 --> 00:28:17,279
I'LL KNOW IT WHEN IT HAPPENS.

530
00:28:19,281 --> 00:28:21,783
WHAT DID YOU MEAN EARLIER
ABOUT RECONSIDERING

531
00:28:21,825 --> 00:28:23,577
SOME DECISIONS YOU'VE MADE?

532
00:28:26,121 --> 00:28:28,957
I'VE SPENT
MY WHOLE LIFE IN SPACE,

533
00:28:28,999 --> 00:28:32,586
GOING FROM ONE PLACE
TO THE NEXT.

534
00:28:32,628 --> 00:28:35,381
SEEING YOU,
I WAS WONDERING,

535
00:28:35,422 --> 00:28:40,135
MAYBE THE NEXT CHALLENGE,
AT LEAST FOR ME,

536
00:28:40,177 --> 00:28:43,055
IS TO STAY IN ONE PLACE
FOR A WHILE.

537
00:28:50,770 --> 00:28:52,314
-HOSHI.
-HMM?

538
00:28:52,356 --> 00:28:55,984
NO WORD YET
FROM TRIP OR T'POL.

539
00:28:56,026 --> 00:28:58,820
IS THERE ANYTHING
I CAN HELP WITH?

540
00:28:58,862 --> 00:29:00,364
SIX OF THE UNIVERSAL TRANSLATORS

541
00:29:00,406 --> 00:29:02,616
STARTED CONFUSING
RIGELIAN WITH ANDORIAN.

542
00:29:02,658 --> 00:29:06,370
THERE'S A GLITCH SOMEWHERE,
BUT I CAN'T FIND IT.

543
00:29:06,412 --> 00:29:07,705
CARRY ON.

544
00:29:16,088 --> 00:29:18,716
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

545
00:29:25,931 --> 00:29:28,726
FRESH OFF THE BOAT?

546
00:29:28,767 --> 00:29:29,976
ONE OF THE S.K. MODELS.

547
00:29:30,018 --> 00:29:31,437
THEY ONLY GIVE THEM
TO GRUBBERS.

548
00:29:34,064 --> 00:29:35,274
I GUESS YOU FOUND ME OUT.

549
00:29:35,315 --> 00:29:37,901
[ LAUGHS ]

550
00:29:37,943 --> 00:29:39,737
JOSIAH.

551
00:29:39,778 --> 00:29:41,405
TURNER.

552
00:29:41,447 --> 00:29:44,032
WHAT BRINGS YOU
TO THIS DUMP SITE?

553
00:29:44,074 --> 00:29:45,325
CHANGE OF SCENERY.

554
00:29:45,367 --> 00:29:47,453
YEAH, THAT'S WHAT
I WAS AFTER, TOO,

555
00:29:47,494 --> 00:29:50,706
ONLY IT WASN'T
THE LANDSCAPE I GOT SICK OF.

556
00:29:50,748 --> 00:29:53,208
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

557
00:29:53,250 --> 00:29:55,210
AT LEAST THERE AREN'T
AS MANY OF THEM UP HERE.

558
00:29:55,252 --> 00:29:56,962
SEEMS LIKE EVERYWHERE YOU GO,

559
00:29:57,003 --> 00:29:59,131
HUMANS ARE GETTING
TO BE AN ENDANGERED SPECIES.

560
00:29:59,172 --> 00:30:00,799
I KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN.

561
00:30:00,840 --> 00:30:03,719
BAD ENOUGH YOU CAN'T
WALK DOWN THE STREET

562
00:30:03,761 --> 00:30:06,513
WITHOUT SOME FREAK SHOW SCARING
THE HELL OUT OF YOUR KIDS.

563
00:30:06,555 --> 00:30:09,642
NOW THE GOVERNMENT'S
MAKING TREATIES WITH THEM.

564
00:30:09,683 --> 00:30:12,102
SOMETIMES I WONDER
WHERE IT'S ALL GONNA END.

565
00:30:12,144 --> 00:30:16,064
IT'S GONNA END WITH HUMAN BEINGS
BECOMING SECOND-CLASS CITIZENS

566
00:30:16,106 --> 00:30:17,524
ON THEIR OWN WORLD.

567
00:30:17,566 --> 00:30:18,942
SOMEONE'S GOT TO MAKE A STAND.

568
00:30:18,984 --> 00:30:22,696
YEAH,
THAT'S HOW I FEEL, TOO.

569
00:30:22,738 --> 00:30:25,783
SOME OF US ARE MEETING
TONIGHT AT 2200.

570
00:30:25,824 --> 00:30:27,326
LEVEL 7, JUNCTION 4.

571
00:30:27,367 --> 00:30:29,369
I THINK YOU'LL LIKE
WHAT WE HAVE TO SAY.

572
00:30:29,411 --> 00:30:31,037
I'LL -- I'LL TRY AND MAKE IT.

573
00:30:31,079 --> 00:30:33,749
I'LL LOOK FOR YOU.

574
00:30:36,084 --> 00:30:37,461
I'VE LEARNED SOMETHING.

575
00:30:40,589 --> 00:30:43,509
ONE OF THE LOCALS
ISN'T VERY FOND OF VULCANS.
YOU WERE SAYING?

576
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:46,303
A DOCTOR FROM ONE
OF THE MEDICAL FACILITIES
WAS FOUND DEAD YESTERDAY.

577
00:30:46,345 --> 00:30:49,181
-THEY THINK IT WAS A CAVE-IN.
-YOU'RE NOT BUYING IT?

578
00:30:49,222 --> 00:30:52,184
HE WORKED AT THE SAME CLINIC
AS SUSAN KHOURI.

579
00:30:53,893 --> 00:30:56,938
I THINK WE EACH KNOW
WHAT WE'RE DOING TONIGHT.

580
00:31:00,734 --> 00:31:03,737
7 MILLION PEOPLE
WIPED OUT BY ALIENS.

581
00:31:03,779 --> 00:31:08,033
-DID THE XINDI EVEN APOLOGIZE?
-NO!

582
00:31:08,074 --> 00:31:10,994
-DID OUR GOVERNMENT
EVER DEMAND AN APOLOGY?
-NO!

583
00:31:11,036 --> 00:31:14,832
AND WHERE ARE THE REPARATIONS
FOR THE FAMILIES
OF THOSE 7 MILLION?

584
00:31:14,873 --> 00:31:17,835
AND NOW THOSE SAME LEADERS
WANT TO FORM A COALITION

585
00:31:17,876 --> 00:31:19,628
WITH TELLARITES, ANDORIANS,

586
00:31:19,670 --> 00:31:22,130
RIGELIANS, CORIDANITES,
AND VULCANS!

587
00:31:22,172 --> 00:31:24,633
VULCANS, WHO NOT TOO LONG AGO

588
00:31:24,675 --> 00:31:28,094
MASSACRED 45 HUMANS
WORKING AT THE EARTH EMBASSY.

589
00:31:28,136 --> 00:31:30,514
NATHAN SAMUELS CLAIMS
THAT FUTURE GENERATIONS

590
00:31:30,556 --> 00:31:33,559
WILL LOOK BACK ON THIS ERA
WITH PRIDE.

591
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:35,686
BUT IF THINGS KEEP GOING
THE WAY THEY'RE GOING,

592
00:31:35,728 --> 00:31:39,064
THERE WON'T BE
ANY FUTURE GENERATIONS,
AT LEAST NOT HUMAN!

593
00:31:39,105 --> 00:31:40,733
[ CROWD AGREEING ]

594
00:31:40,774 --> 00:31:44,944
I LOVE HUMANITY TOO MUCH
TO SIT BY AND LET THAT HAPPEN.

595
00:31:52,327 --> 00:31:54,204
[ ZIPPER OPENS ]

596
00:31:54,246 --> 00:31:56,206
[ BEEPING ]

597
00:32:14,516 --> 00:32:16,560
IT'S ESTIMATED
THAT THERE ARE AT LEAST

598
00:32:16,602 --> 00:32:19,479
5,000 UNREGISTERED
ALIENS ON EARTH.

599
00:32:19,521 --> 00:32:21,857
NOW, ANOTHER STUDY
PUTS THAT FIGURE AT 10,000.

600
00:32:21,899 --> 00:32:26,779
THIS INSANITY
IS THE DIRECT RESULT
OF OUR GOVERNMENT'S POLICY

601
00:32:26,820 --> 00:32:29,030
AND THE ENFORCERS
OF THAT POLICY -- STARFLEET!

602
00:32:29,072 --> 00:32:32,284
[ CROWD SHOUTING ]

603
00:32:32,325 --> 00:32:34,494
WE NEED TO SEND A MESSAGE
TO THE PEOPLE IN POWER.

604
00:32:34,536 --> 00:32:36,162
AND THERE'S SOMEONE HERE TONIGHT

605
00:32:36,204 --> 00:32:38,206
WHO IS GOING TO HELP US
DO JUST THAT.

606
00:32:38,248 --> 00:32:41,376
COMMANDER TUCKER...

607
00:32:41,418 --> 00:32:44,337
OF THE STARSHIP<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

608
00:32:51,637 --> 00:32:54,264
ALL THAT STUFF I SAID
ABOUT LEAVING THE SHIP...

609
00:32:54,306 --> 00:32:57,142
OF COURSE,
IT'S OFF THE RECORD.

610
00:32:57,183 --> 00:33:00,186
WHILE YOU'RE ON DUTY, YOU MIND
IF I STAY HERE AND WORK A BIT?

611
00:33:00,228 --> 00:33:02,689
[ DOOR CHIMES ]

612
00:33:08,737 --> 00:33:10,530
I NEED TO SPEAK TO GANNET.

613
00:33:12,407 --> 00:33:13,784
SOMETHING WRONG?

614
00:33:13,826 --> 00:33:15,076
COME WITH US.

615
00:33:15,118 --> 00:33:17,996
-WHERE?
-WHAT'S GOING ON?

616
00:33:18,037 --> 00:33:20,916
SHE'S NOT HERE TO DO A STORY
ON<i> ENTERPRISE,</i> TRAVIS.

617
00:33:23,502 --> 00:33:28,799
SHE IS A SPY
FOR TERRA PRIME.

618
00:33:34,805 --> 00:33:36,222
[ GASPING ]

619
00:33:36,264 --> 00:33:39,559
-ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
-I THINK SO.

620
00:33:39,601 --> 00:33:42,896
-WHAT DID YOU DO TO HER?
-HEY, HEY.

621
00:33:42,938 --> 00:33:44,564
NOT NEARLY ENOUGH.

622
00:33:44,606 --> 00:33:46,232
IT'S NOT WORTH IT, ROMEO.

623
00:33:46,274 --> 00:33:48,861
JULIET'S IN GOOD HANDS.

624
00:33:50,069 --> 00:33:52,489
THE TWO STAR-CROSSED LOVERS.

625
00:33:52,531 --> 00:33:54,908
I CAN'T HELP BUT WONDER
WHETHER YOUR LITTLE DRAMA

626
00:33:54,950 --> 00:33:58,996
WILL END HAPPIER THAN THAT
FAMOUS DOUBLE-SUICIDE
IN THE MEDIEVAL TOMB.

627
00:33:59,037 --> 00:34:02,415
-WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?
-JOHN FREDERICK PAXTON.

628
00:34:02,457 --> 00:34:04,710
-I RUN THIS FACILITY.
-NOT FOR LONG.

629
00:34:04,751 --> 00:34:06,837
YOU'RE RIGHT, THERE,
COMMANDER.

630
00:34:06,879 --> 00:34:09,548
MY MINING BUSINESS IS ABOUT
TO TAKE A TURN FOR THE WORSE.

631
00:34:09,589 --> 00:34:11,800
DANIEL, GET STARTED.

632
00:34:14,636 --> 00:34:16,221
YOU'RE BEHIND THIS.

633
00:34:16,262 --> 00:34:17,973
BEHIND THIS? NO.

634
00:34:18,015 --> 00:34:20,684
I LEAD THIS,
AND PROUDLY, TOO.

635
00:34:20,726 --> 00:34:23,269
BEFORE YOU ASK,
YOUR CHILD IS SAFE AND SOUND,

636
00:34:23,311 --> 00:34:25,898
FINALLY SLEEPING
THROUGH THE NIGHT.

637
00:34:25,939 --> 00:34:28,608
I FORGOT HOW MUCH TROUBLE
A NEWBORN CAN BE.

638
00:34:28,650 --> 00:34:31,486
-I WANT TO SEE HER.
-NO.

639
00:34:31,528 --> 00:34:34,907
AND "NO" IS A WORD THAT
STARFLEET BETTER GET USED
TO HEARING FROM NOW ON.

640
00:34:34,948 --> 00:34:37,784
BECAUSE UP UNTIL TODAY, IT'S
ALWAYS BEEN "YES," HASN'T IT?

641
00:34:37,826 --> 00:34:40,245
"YES, YES, GO RIGHT AHEAD,
ROAM THE STARS.

642
00:34:40,286 --> 00:34:43,957
"YES, INFORM
POTENTIALLY HOSTILE SPECIES
OF THE WHEREABOUTS OF EARTH.

643
00:34:43,999 --> 00:34:46,001
"YES, ENTRUST THE ENTIRE FUTURE
OF OUR WORLD

644
00:34:46,043 --> 00:34:49,671
"TO NON-HUMAN CREATURES
WHO DON'T EVEN FEEL LIKE WE DO.

645
00:34:49,713 --> 00:34:52,758
"YES, PROMOTE THE TOTAL
DEGRADATION OF MANKIND

646
00:34:52,799 --> 00:34:57,387
BY ENCOURAGING
ALIEN-HUMAN...RELATIONS."

647
00:34:57,429 --> 00:35:03,852
WELL, "YES" IS A WORD
THAT ENDS HERE AND NOW.

648
00:35:03,894 --> 00:35:07,064
I AM RETURNING EARTH
TO ITS RIGHTFUL OWNERS.

649
00:35:07,105 --> 00:35:10,108
I AM GIVING EARTH
BACK TO HUMANITY,

650
00:35:10,149 --> 00:35:11,902
BACK TO HUMAN BEINGS.

651
00:35:11,944 --> 00:35:16,073
IT IS MY LIFE'S WORK.
IT'S WHAT I WAS BORN TO DO.

652
00:35:16,114 --> 00:35:19,200
AND THERE IS NO ONE --
NOT AN ALIEN, NOT A HUMAN --

653
00:35:19,242 --> 00:35:22,996
THAT WILL STOP ME
FROM ACHIEVING IT.

654
00:35:26,374 --> 00:35:28,209
MY FATHER DESIGNED
THIS FACILITY.

655
00:35:28,251 --> 00:35:30,754
HE KNEW THAT MINING
WAS UNPREDICTABLE BUSINESS.

656
00:35:30,796 --> 00:35:33,381
MINES TAP OUT.
VEINS DRY UP.

657
00:35:33,423 --> 00:35:35,425
EVERYONE'S ABOARD, SIR.

658
00:35:35,467 --> 00:35:37,427
GO TO LAUNCH MODE, DANIEL.

659
00:35:37,469 --> 00:35:39,220
YOU'RE AN ENGINEER.

660
00:35:39,262 --> 00:35:42,432
I THINK YOU'LL
APPRECIATE THIS.

661
00:35:42,474 --> 00:35:43,934
[ RUMBLING ]

662
00:35:53,902 --> 00:35:57,155
-TAKE A GOOD LONG LOOK.
-WHERE ARE WE GOING?

663
00:35:57,196 --> 00:36:00,283
FOR YOU, THIS WILL BE LIKE
A WALK ACROSS THE STREET.

664
00:36:00,325 --> 00:36:01,660
[ BEEPING ]

665
00:36:01,701 --> 00:36:03,161
LOCK IT UP.

666
00:36:06,289 --> 00:36:10,085
YOU BETTER HANG ON TO SOMETHING.
SHE GETS A LITTLE RUSTY
OUT OF THE GATE.

667
00:36:27,602 --> 00:36:29,980
YOU RECONFIGURED
YOUR UNIVERSAL TRANSLATOR

668
00:36:30,022 --> 00:36:32,899
TO RECORD MESSAGES FROM
ALL THE OTHER TRANSLATORS.

669
00:36:32,941 --> 00:36:34,860
YOU WERE SPYING
ON THE DELEGATES.

670
00:36:34,901 --> 00:36:38,571
YOU ACCIDENTALLY TRIGGERED
AN I.D. PROTOCOL IN THE NETWORK.

671
00:36:38,613 --> 00:36:40,239
I TRACKED IT BACK
TO THE SOURCE.

672
00:36:40,281 --> 00:36:42,283
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

673
00:36:42,325 --> 00:36:44,494
YOU SURE KNOW WHAT EVERYONE ELSE
WAS TALKING ABOUT.

674
00:36:44,536 --> 00:36:46,913
MAYBE SHE WAS AFTER A STORY.

675
00:36:46,955 --> 00:36:49,541
IT DOESN'T MEAN
SHE WORKED FOR TERRA PRIME.

676
00:36:49,582 --> 00:36:55,338
WE DID A BACKGROUND CHECK.
IN THE LAST MONTH, YOU MADE
THREE TRIPS TO THE LUNAR COLONY.

677
00:36:55,380 --> 00:36:56,589
IS THAT A CRIME?

678
00:36:56,631 --> 00:36:58,633
DEPENDS ON WHAT
YOU'RE DOING THERE.

679
00:36:58,675 --> 00:37:00,510
-I WAS ON ASSIGNMENT.
-FOR?

680
00:37:00,552 --> 00:37:02,054
MY NEWS AGENCY.

681
00:37:02,095 --> 00:37:04,556
YOUR EDITOR CLAIMS
HE NEVER SENT YOU.

682
00:37:04,597 --> 00:37:07,976
LOOK,
IF I'M UNDER ARREST --

683
00:37:08,018 --> 00:37:10,311
TWO OF MY CREWMEN ARE
AT ORPHEUS MINING COMPLEX.

684
00:37:10,353 --> 00:37:13,065
-WE'VE LOST CONTACT WITH THEM.
-I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT YOUR --

685
00:37:13,106 --> 00:37:14,816
ARE THEY IN DANGER?

686
00:37:17,443 --> 00:37:19,320
I WANT TO SPEAK WITH COUNSEL.

687
00:37:21,614 --> 00:37:24,201
NOW.

688
00:37:24,242 --> 00:37:27,370
TAKE HER TO THE BRIG.
GET HER WHOEVER SHE WANTS.

689
00:37:32,500 --> 00:37:33,835
[ DOOR OPENS ]

690
00:37:33,877 --> 00:37:37,630
Bridge to Captain Archer.

691
00:37:37,672 --> 00:37:39,716
I'M SORRY, TRAVIS.

692
00:37:43,095 --> 00:37:44,679
ARCHER.

693
00:37:44,721 --> 00:37:47,224
A large vessel is taking off
from the mining facility.

694
00:37:47,265 --> 00:37:50,018
-CAN YOU IDENTIFY IT?
-Sir, sensors indicate

695
00:37:50,060 --> 00:37:51,519
it is the mining facility.

696
00:37:53,271 --> 00:37:57,192
-[ BEEPING ]
WE'RE BEING HAILED.
-IT'S STARFLEET COMMAND.

697
00:37:57,234 --> 00:37:59,736
IGNORE THEM.
REACTOR STATUS?

698
00:37:59,778 --> 00:38:01,821
-READY.
-YOU'RE GOING TO WARP?

699
00:38:01,863 --> 00:38:04,824
-A 5-SECOND BURST.
-INSIDE THE SYSTEM?

700
00:38:04,866 --> 00:38:06,785
WE'LL BE LUCKY
IF WE DON'T FLY APART.

701
00:38:06,826 --> 00:38:10,622
I PLAN ON LUCK.
GO.

702
00:38:10,663 --> 00:38:12,207
10 SECONDS.

703
00:38:27,472 --> 00:38:30,016
[ metal clanking ]

704
00:38:32,227 --> 00:38:36,564
HAIL THEM.
PURSUIT COURSE, TRAVIS.

705
00:38:36,606 --> 00:38:38,024
AYE.

706
00:38:38,066 --> 00:38:40,401
NO RESPONSE, SIR.

707
00:38:40,443 --> 00:38:43,404
TELL STARFLEET COMMAND
WE'RE GOING AFTER THEM.

708
00:38:51,663 --> 00:38:53,372
WE'RE IN MARS ORBIT.

709
00:38:54,666 --> 00:38:56,626
ALL SYSTEMS FUNCTIONING.

710
00:38:56,668 --> 00:38:59,504
THAT WAS A MAGNIFICENT PIECE
OF FLYING, DANIEL.

711
00:38:59,545 --> 00:39:01,173
THAT'S YET TO COME.

712
00:39:01,214 --> 00:39:02,841
IMPRESS ME AGAIN.

713
00:39:02,882 --> 00:39:04,550
TAKING US DOWN.

714
00:39:13,559 --> 00:39:16,271
LET'S SEE IT.

715
00:39:28,533 --> 00:39:30,535
SLOWING OUR DESCENT.

716
00:39:42,714 --> 00:39:44,507
TIE US IN.

717
00:39:57,562 --> 00:39:59,438
IT'S OURS.

718
00:40:00,732 --> 00:40:03,401
LET'S TAKE IN THE VIEW.

719
00:40:12,869 --> 00:40:15,663
THIS IS WHERE IT ALL BEGINS.

720
00:40:15,705 --> 00:40:17,207
JOSIAH.

721
00:40:18,624 --> 00:40:21,460
-THEY'RE ON THE SURFACE.
-WHERE?

722
00:40:21,502 --> 00:40:23,796
THEY'VE LANDED
NEAR THE VERTERON ARRAY.

723
00:40:23,838 --> 00:40:26,341
IT'S USED TO REDIRECT COMETS.

724
00:40:26,383 --> 00:40:30,011
-[ BEEPING ]
-THEY'RE SENDING A SUBSPACE
MESSAGE ON ALL FREQUENCIES.

725
00:40:33,306 --> 00:40:35,350
<i>MY NAME IS</i>
<i>JOHN FREDERICK PAXTON.</i>

726
00:40:35,392 --> 00:40:38,311
<i>I'VE JUST TAKEN OVER</i>
<i>THE VERTERON ARRAY ON MARS.</i>

727
00:40:38,353 --> 00:40:42,565
<i>I CAN NOW FIRE ON ANY SHIP</i>
<i>OR FACILITY IN THE SYSTEM.</i>

728
00:40:42,607 --> 00:40:44,317
[ BEEPING ]

729
00:40:50,615 --> 00:40:52,700
HE'S TARGETED EARTH'S MOON.

730
00:41:00,083 --> 00:41:02,501
<i>I HAVE NO INTENTION</i>
<i>OF USING THIS WEAPON AGAIN,</i>

731
00:41:02,543 --> 00:41:06,381
<i>PROVIDED THAT EVERY SINGLE</i>
<i>NON-HUMAN IN OUR SYSTEM</i>

732
00:41:06,423 --> 00:41:08,341
<i>LEAVES IMMEDIATELY.</i>

733
00:41:08,383 --> 00:41:10,385
<i>A NEW ERA IS AT HAND,</i>

734
00:41:10,427 --> 00:41:13,596
<i>AN ERA WHICH WILL</i>
<i>EXPOSE THE CONCEPT</i>

735
00:41:13,638 --> 00:41:15,140
<i>OF INTERSPECIES UNITY</i>

736
00:41:15,181 --> 00:41:17,392
<i>AS AN ABSOLUTE</i>
<i>AND VICIOUS LIE.</i>

737
00:41:17,434 --> 00:41:19,185
<i>AN ERA THAT WILL WITNESS</i>
<i>THE ADVENT</i>

738
00:41:19,227 --> 00:41:21,813
<i>OF A HUMAN-CENTRIC</i>
<i>CONSCIOUSNESS</i>

739
00:41:21,854 --> 00:41:25,483
THAT WILL PLACE OUR WORLD
BEFORE ALL OTHERS.

740
00:41:25,524 --> 00:41:30,113
AS OF THIS MOMENT,
MANKIND CASTS OFF THE SHACKLES

741
00:41:30,155 --> 00:41:32,240
OF ALIEN INTERFERENCE,

742
00:41:32,282 --> 00:41:35,910
AND NOW DETERMINES
ITS OWN FATE.

743
00:41:35,952 --> 00:41:40,039
<i>TERRA PRIME...FOREVER.</i>
